desc: Rhino Rescue CUF IFAK, First-Aid Kits,EDC Trauma,Combat,Survival Kit, First Aid For Tactical Deskripsi : Model Number : CUF-Care Under Fire  Brand Name : RHINO RESCUE  Origin : Mainland China  Size : 16*12*5.5cm  CUF-Care Under Fire Care Under Fire (CUF) is medical attention provided by the first responder or combatant to arrive at the scene of injury during an in-progress firefight.  Typically, in a Care Under Fire situation, available medical equipment is limited to that carried by the casualty in his or her individual first-aid kit (IFAK) or by the medical provider in his or her aid bag.  Remember: If you can do only ONE thing for the casualty, identify and stop life-threatening bleeding, and keep them from bleeding to death.
